    S:gt.blockmachines.dysonswarm.name=Ядро группы роя Дайсона
    S:gt.blockmachines.dysonswarm.tooltip=Machine Type: §eDyson Swarm§r\n§o%s\nPut Dyson Swarm Modules in the Input Bus(es) to send them to the next star.\nOutputs §a10,000,000*§9§lD§r §7EU/t per module up to §a10,000\nEach hour, §6§lI§r§a * (2 * 0.066) / (exp(-0.00005 * (§6§lI§r§a - 1)) + exp(0.00003 * §b§lC§r§a)) §7of modules are destroyed.\n§b§lC§r§bomputation/s§r, §6§lI§r§6nitial module amount, §9§lD§r§9imension-dependent factor §7(check quest for values)\nRequires §a3,600,000L/h §7of Gelid Cryotheum.\nR-Click with a Plunger to extract as many Modules to your inventory as possible.\nSneaking will dump the rest on the ground.\n§aSupports TecTech Multi-Amp and Laser Hatches!\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
