    S:gt.blockmachines.largemolecularassembler.name=Большой молекулярный сборщик
    S:gt.blockmachines.largemolecularassembler.tooltip=Machine Type: §eMolecular Assembler, LMA§r\nNeeds a Data Orb to be placed in the controller\nBasic: §a16§7 EU/t, unaffected by overclocking\nCrafting: §a64§7 EU/t, Finish §f2§7 Jobs in §f1§7s\nThe first two Overclocks:\n-Reduce the Finish time to §f0.5§7s and §f0.25§7s\nSubsequent Overclocks:\n-Double the number of Jobs finished at once\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
