    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.adv.vacuumfurnace.tooltip=Machine Type: §eVacuum Furnace, Dehydrator§r\nFactory Grade Vacuum Furnace\n§64§7 Parallels\n§a220%§7 Speed\n§b50%§7 EU Usage\nCan toggle the operation temperature with a Screwdriver\nAll Dehydrator recipes are Low Temp recipes\nReduces §bEU Usage§7 by §f5%§7 every §c900K§7 above the recipe requirement\nEvery §c1800K§7 over the recipe requirement grants 1 §dPerfect Overclock\n§5500 §7Pollution per second\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
