    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.autoclave.tooltip=Machine Type: §eAutoclave§r\n§612§7 Parallels per §fItem Pipe Casing§7 Tier\n§a+25%§7 Speed per §fHeating Coil§7 Tier\n§b-8.33%§7 EU Usage per §fPipe Casing§7 Tier\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines\nAdded by: §a§bVolence§r§7
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.autoclave.tooltip_secondary=§fDimensions: §67§7x§67§7x§69§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) §c(Hollow)\n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front bottom center\n§6   128x §r§7Pressure Containment Casings (minimum)\n§6   42x §r§7Any Tiered Glass\n§6   7x §r§7Item Pipe Casings (tiered)\n§6   14x §r§7Pipe Casings (tiered)\n§6   7x §r§7Heating Coils (tiered)\n§6   42x §r§7PTFE Frame\n§f   Input Bus: §7Any Pressure Containment Casing\n§f   Output Bus: §7Any Pressure Containment Casing\n§f   Input Hatch: §7Any Pressure Containment Casing\n§f   Output Hatch: §7Any Pressure Containment Casing\n§f   Energy Hatch: §7Any Pressure Containment Casing\n§f   Maintenance Hatch: §7Any Pressure Containment Casing\n   Uses sub channel §6glass§r§7 for §6Glass Tier\n   Uses sub channel §6item_pipe§r§7 for §6Item Pipe Casing Tier\n   Uses sub channel §6pipe§r§7 for §6Pipe Casing Tier\n   Uses sub channel §6coil§r§7 for §6Heating Coils Tier\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
