    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.defusioncrafter.tooltip_secondary=§fDimensions: §65§7x§610§7x§65§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) \n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front bottom center\n§6   19x §r§7Naquadah Alloy Fusion Casing (minimum)\n§f   Fusion Coil Block: §7Center pillar\n§f   Fusion Machine Casing: §7Touching Fusion Coil Block at every side\n§f   Tiered Fusion Casing: §7Rings (5x5 hollow) at layer 4 and 7\n   Bloody Ichorium for tier 1, Draconium for tier 2, etc\n   To use tier 3 + you have to use fusion casing MK II\n§f   Input Bus: §7Any bottom casing\n§f   Input Hatch: §7Any bottom casing\n§f   Output Bus: §7Any bottom casing\n§f   Output Hatch: §7Any bottom casing\n§f   Energy Hatch: §7Any bottom casing\n§f   Maintenance Hatch: §7Any bottom casing\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
