    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.mmuplink.name=Квантовый канал манипулятора материи
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.mmuplink.tooltip=Machine Type: §eMatter Manipulator Quantum Uplink§r\nInterdimensional and infinite range uplink for matter manipulators.\nAllows manipulators to convert plans into AE patterns.\nConnects directly to an ME system via a §6Quantum Uplink ME Connector Hatch§7.\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nConsumes 1A ZPM while active.\nMust be fed with plasma via an input hatch.\nTransfers to/from the manipulator cost 131,072 EU in plasma per item or per bucket.\nInsert a compatible manipulator in the controller slot while the machine is running to bind it to the uplink.\n§aSupports TecTech Multi-Amp and Laser Hatches!\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines\nAdded by: §a§9Recursive Pineapple§r§7
