    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.oredrill4.tooltip=Machine Type: §eMiner, MBM§r\nUse a Screwdriver to configure working area\nMaximum area is 18x18 chunks (288x288 blocks)\nIn chunk mode, working area center is the chunk corner nearest to the drill\nUse Soldering iron to turn off chunk mode\nUse Wire Cutter to toggle replacing mined blocks with cobblestone\nGives ~3x as much crushed ore vs normal processing\nFortune bonus of 7. Only works on small ores\nMinimum energy hatch tier: §9IV§r\nBase cycle time: 15 ticks\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
