    S:gt.blockmachines.orewashingplant.controller.tier.single.tooltip=Machine Type: §eOre Washer, Simple Washer§r\n§64§7 Parallels per §fVoltage§7 Tier\n§a500%§7 Speed\n§8100%§7 EU Usage\nCan be configured with a screwdriver to also be used as Simple Washer\nAlways requires an Input Hatch full of water to refill structure\nNeed to be filled with water\nWill automatically fill water from Input Hatch\n§5100 §7Pollution per second\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines\nStructure by: §a§6ya9yu§r§7
