    S:gt.blockmachines.quantumforcetransformer.controller.tier.single.tooltip=Machine Type: §eQuantum Force Transformer, QFT§r\nAllows Complex processing lines to be performed instantly in one step\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§dPulse Manipulator§7 Tier determines maximum recipe tier\nEvery recipe requires a specific §dcatalyst§7\n§dCatalysts§7 have to be placed in a Bulk Catalyst Housing\nGains §61§7 Parallel per §dCatalyst§7\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§aShielding Core§7 Tier determines §aFocusing§7 Bonuses\nPut a circuit in the controller to specify the focused output, based on NEI order\nIf Input Separation is on: put the circuit in the circuit slot of the bus\nConsumes 4 * §aFocus Tier§7 * sqrt(§6parallels§7) L §9Neptunium Plasma§7 to §afocus§7\nThe better the §aFocus Tier§7, the §astronger§7 the effect\n§aFocused§7 Output will have its §bprobability boosted§7, with other output's being reduced evenly by the total boost\nConsumes 4 * §aFocus Tier§7 * sqrt(§6parallels§7) L §2Fermium Plasma§7 to §2boost all outputs\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nUse a screwdriver to enable §9Fluid mode\nFluid mode turns all possible outputs into their fluid variant, if avaliable\nThis machine can run recipes regardless of tier, if given enough energy\n§aSupports TecTech Multi-Amp and Laser Hatches!\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines\nAdded by: §a§9§lBlue§b§lWeabo§r§7 & §a§aSteelux§r§7
    S:gt.blockmachines.quantumforcetransformer.controller.tier.single.tooltip_secondary=§fDimensions: §615§7x§621§7x§615§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) §c(Hollow)\n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front bottom center\n§6   80x §r§7Bulk Production Frame (minimum)\n§6   177x §r§7Quantum Force Conductor (minimum)\n§6   224x §r§7Force Field Glass (minimum)\n§6   236x §r§7Pulse Manipulators (minimum) (tiered)\n§6   142x §r§7Shielding Cores (minimum) (tiered)\n§f   Input Bus: §7§9Bottom§7 Layer\n§f   Input Hatch: §7§9Bottom§7 Layer\n§f   Output Hatch: §7§bTop§7 Layer\n§f   Output Bus: §7§bTop§7 Layer\n§f   Energy Hatch: §7§9Bottom§7 Layer\n   §fBulk Catalyst Housing: §9Bottom§7 Layer\n   Uses sub channel §6shielding§r§7 for §6Shielding Tier\n   Uses sub channel §6manipulator§r§7 for §6Manipulator Tier\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
