    S:gt.blockmachines.supercriticalsteamturbine.tooltip_secondary=§fDimensions: §63§7x§63§7x§66§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) \n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front center\n§6   8x§7 - §616x §r§7SC Turbine Casing\n§6   14x §r§7PBI Frame Box\n§6   12x §r§7PBI Pipe Casing\n§f   Dynamo Hatch: §7Back center\n§f   Maintenance Hatch: §7Any SC Turbine Casing except the front 8\n§f   Input Hatch: §7Any SC Turbine Casing except the front 8\n§f   Output Hatch: §7Any SC Turbine Casing except the front 8\n§f   Air: §73x3 area in front of controller\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
